`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
The batch preview widget follows the two-phase editor pattern: editor (mrr-qtk.2) → preview → dispatch (mrr-qtk.4). The preview computes change detection by comparing staged reviewers against each MR's current `ReviewerInfo` slice, keyed by `Username`. This ensures the dispatch in the next task can skip API calls for MRs where nothing actually changes.
